longBusinessSummary: Ensurge, Inc., a mining holding company, engages in the exploration and development of gold properties in Guyana, South America. It also explores for diamond and other precious metals. The company was formerly known as iShopper.com, Inc. and changed its name to Ensurge, Inc. in October 2000. Ensurge, Inc. was founded in 1985 and is based in Salt Lake City, Utah.
